      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WEEKEND SCOTCH (2) is in top form lately including an excellent win at this track in 17.24 two back then backing it up with a 17.49 victory at this track over 300m latest. Running fast times and looks the one to beat again. RIPPED RACCOON (3) had won three in a row before finishing second (17.52) last time at this track. Has never been out of the money in six starts this course and distance. The form out of his last race has been franked. Expected to be in the finish again. TINKER AMINA (8) finished fifth last time (23.66) at The Gardens after winning at her previous two outings. Has a good record here at this journey. Has ability and can atone. SHE'S SILKY (6) has claims fresh from a recent placing.",
